name: NFT Acai Bowl
description: When I ordered an acai bowl this morning, the Thai lady selling me asked "what do you want to be written on it?". I said "NFT". She said "Ok. But it's not a bad word is it? We can't do bad words". I said "No, it's a great word". She said "Ok!" and got to making it. A moment later she brought the bowl and I took the picture. That's how the NFT acai bowl with some mint became an NFT Acai Bowl minted. Magic of words.
